No. 977. No. 1093,

Mise.

E. I. Du Pont de Nemours & Co., Inc. v. Maloney; and Maloney v. E. I. Du Pont de Nemours & Co. William H. Allen for petitioner in No. 977 and for respondent in No. 1093, Mise. Henry Lincoln Johnson, Jr., for petitioner in No. 1093, Mise.

C. A. D. C. Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Harlan took no part in the consideration or decision of these petitions.

Reported below: 122 U. S. App. D. C. 268, 352 P. 2d 936.
